title: 2 Korinthte 8:8
body: Huai leng ka lamet louh bang un ahih ua, Pathian deihlam in, amau mahmah Toupa kiang ah leh kou kiang ah a kipe masa phot ua;

title: Laazilna om non ding
body:
Zingchiang April 12, dak 6:00 Pm in tuailai pawl lazilna om non ding, tuailaite a tam theilam kuan non siausiau ding in i ki ngen ahi.

- Music Secretary
